# CODEOWNERS — Dark Factory Governance Platform (ai-submodule)
#
# Defines code ownership for pull request review requirements.
# The org ruleset "Pull Request - Reviewer" enforces require_code_owner_review.
#
# NOTE: The Dark Factory governance workflow approves PRs as github-actions[bot].
# Bot approvals do NOT satisfy code owner review requirements. For the agentic
# loop to merge PRs without human intervention, either:
#   1. Disable require_code_owner_review in the org/repo ruleset, OR
#   2. Add a machine user (not bot) as a code owner who can approve, OR
#   3. Use a GitHub App with bypass permissions for the branch protection rule
# See governance/docs/repository-configuration.md for details.

# Default owner — all files not matched by more specific rules
* @SET-Apps/approvers

# CI/CD workflows require DevOps review
/.github/workflows/ @SET-Apps/devops_engineers

# Infrastructure files require DevOps review
/infra/ @SET-Apps/devops_engineers

# Governance submodule changes
/.ai @SET-Apps/approvers
